Quote:  <i>Blue pugaree</i>. (Gen. pl) A military policeman: New Zealand soldiers': 1915-18. Ex the distinctive colour of their hat-bands. [Beale P8 draws attention to the name <i>Red Caps</i> and the nickname Bluey for a redheaded person]
